   <br /> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="line-height:107%">With the recent challenges of COVID-19 largely affecting the restaurant industry, I understand how important it is for restaurants to provide a safe and hygienic facility for customers and employees. As many restaurants now are reopening, I wanted to check-in and let you know Citron Hygiene is here to help.</span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:107%">The majority of patrons and employees now have heightened awareness of proper hygiene measures – meaning businesses need to ensure all areas of their restaurant are adequately prepared to limit the spread of viruses and bacteria. From my experience, one of the most commonly overlooked areas of a restaurant is the washroom, with 56% of people saying they will not return to a business with poor washroom hygiene.</span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:107%">With so much to look after, including new regulations from government agencies, the last thing your restaurant should have to worry about is the hygiene conditions of your washroom. For over 45 years, Citron Hygiene has provided innovative hygiene services that address all areas of your restaurant, including the washroom. Our industry experience allows us to focus on the key bacteria hot spots of your washroom including; the toilet, sanitary disposal bin, dispensers, sink and the floor.</span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:107%">To better explain how Citron Hygiene is here to help your restaurant, I have attached an industry paper that will explain the measures we take to protect staff and customers of the restaurant industry. I would like to set a time to further discuss what hygiene service could benefit the health of your business so you don’t just reopen, but stay open! &nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:107%">Does <span style="color:#d35400;">MONTH</span>, <span style="color:#c0392b;">DATE</span> at <span style="color:#c0392b;">0:00</span> work for you to review some of Citron Hygiene’s preventative hygiene measures?<br /> <br /> <b><span style="color:#c0392b;">REMEMBER TO INSERT THE APPROPRIATE MEETING DETAILS ABOVE!!!</span>&nbsp;</b></span></span></span> 
   <br /> 
   <br /> <span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;">Thank you,</span> 
   <br /> 
   <br /> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">{{{Sender.Name}}}</span></span> 
